item.title: How to teleport down? like underground?
item.dc:creator: @m_st3r8 m st3r8
item.description:
@m_st3r8 wrote:

Wow you all fail !!! when you go “underground” you are atually only teleported somewere on the map. for example, the grave digging random event is really close to the vampire room at draynor mansion (you would think its udnerground) so when you click on a latter, it only teleports you somewere else, if you decrease the height you would just be under ground in a sense that the ground is above you, and nothing is under you. if that doesnt make sense, imagine that all stairs and latters in the game do nothing more than teleport you to a different place on the map.

to answer your question, just go in the notes folder (if you have one) and go to coord list (if you have one) if you don’t have it just google it. anyways, search for hill giants. if that doesnt work just look for varrock underground or something like that.
